claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A table presenting percentages of solicited local and systemic adverse events (categorized as any, moderate, severe) reported by subjects in multiple clinical studies of a vaccine. does not support the claim: the table only reports safety data on adverse events and contains no information on antigenic matching to WHO- or FDA-selected flu strains
